Package com.example.hashcache.models.database

Class TestPlayerDatabase

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.hashcache.models.database.TestPlayerDatabase
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IPlayerDatabase
    public class TestPlayerDatabase
extends java.lang.Object
implements IPlayerDatabase
    The TestPlayerDatabase class represents a test database of players that can be interacted with. It implements the IPlayerDatabase interface which defines the methods that can be performed on the database.
